{"ts":"2026-06-26T17:03:10.673Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"submit_and_exit","toolCallId":"3y3i697v","input":{"summary":"I have successfully upgraded the 'Talk to Agent' frontend-only experience at `/build/talk`.\n\n### Design Plan & Core Accomplishments:\n1. **Interactive Multi-Gate Guided Form**: Built an enterprise-grade guided console split into 3 logical 'gates' for user convenience and clean layout:\n   - **Gate 1: Operational Friction**: Features a custom-styled, real-time character-validated `<textarea>` (minimum 15 characters, maximum 1000) with clickable, interactive enterprise examples (such as 'Employees spend too much time searching for information' and 'Too many manual processes across departments') that prefill the input.\n   - **Gate 2: Domain & Scale**: Custom option cards with glowing borders for Industry selection (Finance, Retail, Healthcare, Energy, Government, Technology) and Company Size brackets.\n   - **Gate 3: Strategic Parameters**: Dropdown selections for Geography (optional), Urgency (optional), Function/Team (optional), and Current AI Stage (optional).\n2. **Sovereign Compile Terminal State**: Added a highly interactive compiler state with custom rotating/pulse SVG radar visuals and real-time step animations mimicking client-side execution logs.\n3. **Smart Local Preview Results**: Formulated a beautiful, bento-grid results layout computed deterministically in-browser. It is clearly labeled with a prominent 'FRONTEND LOCAL PREVIEW' warning, highlighting that no data is retained or transit-loaded.\n   - **Proposed Direction**: Detailed, editorial concept brief customized to the user's selected domain and team. Includes deterministic expected ROI estimates.\n   - **Suggested Squad**: Highlighted custom technical agent profiles (e.g. `AS-09 Balance Auditor`, `MD-05 Privacy Watchdog`, etc.) with in-memory active statuses.\n   - **Indicative Timeline**: Chronological narrative-timeline map showing a 90-day execution framework customized to selected Urgency and AI Stage values.\n4. **GFF Engagement Methodology Side Panel**: Designed a highly polished enterprise sidebar explaining how GFF's operational pillars (Garage, Foundry, Factory) sequentially engage to support and scale active workloads.\n5. **Call to Actions**: Integrated premium, modern CTAs leading to `/build/blueprint` (Generate Deep Blueprint) and `/contact` (Secure Technical Sync).\n6. **Mobile Responsive & Accessible Design**: Optimized touch controls, proper HTML `<label>` element links, focus ring styles, keyboard navigation friendliness, logical heading structures, and custom error validation.\n7. **Code Quality**: Code has been verified with `npm run lint` and passes with exactly 0 errors and 0 warnings. No landing page files or global slug folders were modified.","verified":true}}}
